Index to sequences related to the complexity of n
mathematica: cpx[1] = 1; cpx[k_] := cpx[k] = Min[Sequence @@ Table[cpx[i] + cpx[k-i], {i, 1, k/2}], Sequence @@ Table[cpx[d] + cpx[k/d], {d, Divisors[k][[2 ;; -2]]}]];
